        "action": "Introduce grants for home battery storage systems",
        "additional_details": "This could also reduce C02 output helping towards Government C02 targets.\r\n\r\nOur reliance on foreign fuels such as gas and oil, has been driving up household energy costs and this will become more of an issue with the current war in Ukraine, and deteriorating relations with Russia.",
